T*
(roots.) Tj
T*
(2. Identify the exact idea in recognizing quadratic form and selecting a suitable) Tj
T*
(solving method that the question is testing.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct method for Quadratic Equations step by step without skipping) Tj
T*
(reasoning.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the final answer and explain why it is correct.) Tj
